org.sensorhub.api.persistence

Class DataKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sensorhub.api.persistence.DataKey
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ObsKey

    public class DataKey
extends Object

    Base class for all keys associated to data records in SensorHub. Keys are used to store time stamped data records in storage.

    Since:
    Nov 6, 2010
    Author:

    • Field Detail

      • recordType

        public String recordType
        ID of record type (i.e. maps to a record structure definition).
        This field cannot be null.

      • timeStamp

        public double timeStamp
        Time stamp of data record (e.g. measurement sampling time).
        If value is NaN, data record will never be selected when filtering on time stamp

      • producerID

        public String producerID
        ID of data producer (i.e. the entity that produced the data record).
        If value is null, data record will never be selected when filtering on producer ID
